{"tid":1410321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港歷史一刻","createTime":"2019-08-05T01:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T01:32:59.000Z","uid":151507,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"451fb8100d6448137b1ea30c9ad229ca24ae4c12","tid":1410321,"uid":151507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:17:46.000Z","msg":"【0914】現時港鐵共有八條線服務受阻。<br />\n<br />\n港島線：灣仔站往返鰂魚涌站服務暫停<br />\n荃灣線：尖沙咀站往返荃灣站服務暫停<br />\n觀塘線：黃埔站往返觀塘站服務暫停<br />\n將軍澳線：北角至調景嶺及將軍澳至康城服務暫停<br />\n西鐵線：紅磡站往返柯士甸站、錦上路站往返屯門站服務暫停<br />\n東鐵線：九龍塘站往返羅湖站及落馬洲站服務暫停<br />\n東涌線：南昌站往返青衣站服務暫停<br />\n機場快線：全線服務暫停<br />\n<br />\n另外，因應快閃堵路及各路面不合作運動，不同地區都有交通擠塞，部分巴士線需改道行駛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099baf9ca69aaa360193c32cd14043a991c1b3ab","tid":1410321,"uid":16372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:20:46.000Z","msg":"香港人出黎呀！"},{"pid":"9b144cf3585385ed96b37119c389d4a927ec9882","tid":1410321,"uid":151507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:32:00.000Z","msg":"齊齊唔返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922e709ae3bfacb08c193943cbaa3808f8d0b6c2","tid":1410321,"uid":91397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:32:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}